{"body": "If anyone would like work around this bug until rails developers finally takes care about it, then:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n# config/initializers/fix_rails_2076\r\nrequire 'builder'\r\n\r\nmodule Builder\r\n  class XmlBase\r\n    # We aren't under Ruby 1.9?\r\n    unless ::String.method_defined?(:encode)\r\n      def _escape(text)\r\n        text.to_xs\r\n      end\r\n    end\r\n  end\r\nend\r\n```\r\n\r\nTerrible, but works.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/4352314", "created_at": "2012-03-06T20:19:41Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2076#issuecomment-4352314", "updated_at": "2012-03-06T20:19:41Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2076, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/hron84", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/18fddee34c2ec9f584f198aa4785d6f0?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F361324587accd8afa09767b9c086acb0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/received_events", "gravatar_id": "18fddee34c2ec9f584f198aa4785d6f0", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "hron84", "type": "User", "id": 88636, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hron84/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52384882bd3543c15101116c"}, "id": 4352314, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2076"}
